{"root":{"data":{"id":"d2gipcwsmc00","created":1720072193323,"text":"仪表供气"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2gismykr5s0","created":1720072450291,"text":"1.气源质量"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2giu5glowo0","created":1720072568927,"text":"气源系统露点应比当地最低气温低10℃"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2giu5u3sgw0","created":1720072569743,"text":"空气含尘粒径不应大于3微米，含尘量小于1mg/m3"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gizim5o5k0","created":1720072989382,"text":"油含量小于1ppm"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2gisnhp6xs0","created":1720072451447,"text":"2.气源装置"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2gjb9ouj7k0","created":1720073910323,"text":"工艺吹扫用气不得从仪表用气上取气"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gjb9z3uao0","created":1720073910944,"text":"仪表总耗气量宜采用汇总的方式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2gjrr9zk7k0","created":1720075202434,"text":"每台控制阀耗气量0.7Nm3/h~1.5Nm3/h"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gjrrobu340","created":1720075203301,"text":"控制室气动仪表每台耗气量0.5Nm3/h~1.0Nm3/h"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gjrrvni9k0","created":1720075203744,"text":"现场气动仪表每台耗气量1.0Nm3/h"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gjrs4iqko0","created":1720075204280,"text":"切断阀的耗气量根据气缸容积和每小时动作次数计算"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gk8ttavp40","created":1720076540146,"text":"气源容量按照公式：qv1=qv2(2+A)计算"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2gjba7ok4o0","created":1720073911462,"text":"气源送到各装置的压力范围宜为：500kpa(G)~700kpa(G)，低于规定下限应设置声光报警"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gkc4sh0dc0","created":1720076799133,"text":"安全供气"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2gkcjt09ew0","created":1720076831817,"text":"仪表供气管网压力低宜报警，压力超低宜联锁"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gkckbzxb40","created":1720076832965,"text":"输出总管设置在线露点仪，信号输出到控制室"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"d2gkef1qhe80","created":1720076978189,"text":"备用气源：储气罐、空压机"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2gkf3wduao0","created":1720077032285,"text":"储气罐容积计算，计算公式：V=60*qv1*tp0(p1-p2)具体看规范"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"d2gisnpwn680","created":1720072451943,"text":"现场仪表供气方式"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"d2gkoit514o0","created":1720077770018,"te